# Switch2itech Backend API Documentation

This document outlines the available API endpoints for the Switch2itech backend.

## Base URL
`http://localhost:5000/api` (or regulated by environment variables)

---

## ð Authentication (`/auth`)

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required | Role |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| POST | `/register` | Register a new user | No | - |
| POST | `/login` | Login and receive HttpOnly cookie | No | - |
| POST | `/logout` | Logout and clear cookie | No | - |
| GET | `/me` | Get current authenticated user details | Yes | Any |

---

## ðĨ User Management (`/users`)

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required | Role |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| GET | `/` | Get all users (Filter: `?role=`) | Yes | Admin, Manager |
| GET | `/:id` | Get specific user profile | Yes | Any |
| PATCH | `/:id` | Update user role | Yes | Admin |

---

## ðïļ Project Management (`/projects`)

### Projects
| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required | Role |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| GET | `/` | Get all projects | Yes | Any |
| POST | `/` | Create project (Supports multipart: `coverImage`, `demoVideo`) | Yes | Admin, Manager |
| GET | `/:id` | Get specific project details | Yes | Any |
| PATCH | `/:id` | Update project details | Yes | Admin, Manager |
| DELETE | `/:id` | Delete project | Yes | Admin |
| PATCH | `/:id/assign` | Assign clients, manager, or team (Body: `{ clients, manager, teamMembers, action }`) | Yes | Admin |

### Milestones
| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required | Role |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| GET | `/:projectId/milestones` | Get all milestones for a project | Yes | Any |
| POST | `/:projectId/milestones` | Create a new milestone | Yes | Admin, Manager |
| PATCH | `/:projectId/milestones/:milestoneId` | Update milestone | Yes | Admin, Manager |
| DELETE | `/:projectId/milestones/:milestoneId` | Delete milestone | Yes | Admin |
| PATCH | `/:projectId/milestones/:milestoneId/assign` | Assign milestone to user | Yes | Admin, Manager |

### Modules
| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required | Role |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| GET | `/:projectId/milestones/:milestoneId/modules` | Get modules in a milestone | Yes | Any |
| POST | `/:projectId/milestones/:milestoneId/modules` | Create module | Yes | Admin, Manager |
| PATCH | `/:projectId/milestones/:milestoneId/modules/:moduleId` | Update module status/details | Yes | Admin, Manager, Developer |
| PATCH | `/:projectId/milestones/:milestoneId/modules/:moduleId/assign` | Assign module to developer | Yes | Admin, Manager |

### Tasks
| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required | Role |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| GET | `/:projectId/milestones/:milestoneId/modules/:moduleId/tasks` | Get tasks in a module | Yes | Any |
| POST | `/:projectId/milestones/:milestoneId/modules/:moduleId/tasks` | Create task | Yes | Any |
| PATCH | `/:projectId/milestones/:milestoneId/modules/:moduleId/tasks/:taskId` | Update task | Yes | Any |
| DELETE | `/:projectId/milestones/:milestoneId/modules/:moduleId/tasks/:taskId` | Delete task | Yes | Admin, Manager |
| PATCH | `/:projectId/milestones/:milestoneId/modules/:moduleId/tasks/:taskId/assign` | Assign task to developer | Yes | Admin, Manager |

### Project FAQs
| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required | Role |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| POST | `/:id/faqs` | Add FAQ to project | Yes | Admin, Manager |
| PATCH | `/:id/faqs/:faqId` | Update FAQ | Yes | Admin, Manager |
| DELETE | `/:id/faqs/:faqId` | Delete FAQ | Yes | Admin, Manager |

---

## ðĶ Product Management (`/products`)

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required | Role |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| GET | `/` | Get all products | No | - |
| GET | `/:id` | Get specific product | No | - |
| POST | `/` | Create product (Multipart: `image`, `video`, `thumbnail`) | Yes | Admin |
| PUT | `/:id` | Update product | Yes | Admin |
| DELETE | `/:id` | Delete product | Yes | Admin |
| POST | `/:id/faqs` | Add FAQ | Yes | Admin |
| PATCH | `/:id/faqs/:faqId` | Update FAQ | Yes | Admin |
| DELETE | `/:id/faqs/:faqId` | Delete FAQ | Yes | Admin |

---

## ðŽ Testimonials (`/testimonials`)

| Method | Endpoint | Description | Auth Required | Role |
| :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- | :--- |
| GET | `/` | List testimonials (`?approved=true`, `?project=`, `?product=`) | No | - |
| GET | `/:id` | Get single testimonial | No | - |
| POST | `/` | Submit a new testimonial/review | Yes | Any |
| PATCH | `/:id` | Edit own testimonial or any if admin | Yes | Owner, Admin |
| PATCH | `/:id/approve` | Approve/feature a testimonial | Yes | Admin |
| DELETE | `/:id` | Remove testimonial | Yes | Admin |

---

